casebody.data:
Friday, December 27, 1996

MOTION DOCKET

96-42. Pennsylvania Power Co. v. Lake Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 95-K-841. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals.

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, effective December 26, 1996, that this cause be, and hereby is, consolidated with Supreme Court case Nos. 96-38, 96-39, 96-40, 96-41 and 96-43.
